            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Error spam is a general issue that will be fixed by changing our UI for messages, so that a flood of message is capped at e.g. 10 lines and further messages are indicated by a `+99 messages` note. https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/22478\r\n\r\n\"session load plugins\" are irrelevant. If there is still a specific bug with `diagnostic.lua` (the original issue here), open a new issue and describe that bug specifically. \r\n\r\nThe `_changetracking.lua` issue is unrelated (why report it here?). https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/28575",
